data.description: Must see Bungalow with charm. New roofs plus updates located in convenient area! Living room features an artificial fireplace flanked by built-in bookcases and crown molding plus a beautiful plaster ceiling detail, crown moldings also present in formal dining room with built-in china cabinet. Kitchen has been nicely updated and offers lots of storage in the walk-in pantry; refreshed bathroom; two main floor bedrooms plus two more upstairs -- HUGE newly added master bedroom; side bedroom plus loft room at top of the steps -- great home office or hobby space! Backyard has a newer privacy fence, garage and gravel driveway which can accommodate 4 cars! Newer high efficiency furnace; power vented water heater. Home has been weatherized! Sizes estimated.
